---
title: HelloHero: Teriyaki Beef & Veggie Noodles with Capsicum & Broccoli
description: This bowl is oodles of fun with noodles for all. The best part, that’s really going to set a smile on your face, is the saucy teriyaki ginger beef and veggies. To finish it off, we may not have glitter but a sprinkle of crispy shallots is just as great!

